# DPAH (Data Patterns Agents Hub) — Complete Application Documentation

## 1. Executive Summary

DPAH is an **enterprise AI agent orchestration platform** built with FastAPI that provides role-based access control (RBAC) agent permissions across multiple business collections (RMS, SCM, HRMS, FINANCE, MRR). The application implements a sophisticated **LangGraph-based workflow** that routes user requests through permission-gated agent nodes (Creator, Reviewer, Approver) with SSE streaming, form widgets, RAG context, file upload processing, and generative UI capabilities.

