### 7.1 RMS Workflow Graph

**Location:** [`workflows/rms_workflow/graph.py`](app/workflows/rms_workflow/graph.py)

```
User Request
    │
    ▼
┌─────────────────┐
│ parse_intent    │ → Infer persona from keywords
└────────┬────────┘
         │
         ▼
┌─────────────────┐
│ permission_check│ → Validate user has this persona
└────────┬────────┘
         │
    ┌────┴────┐
    │         │
    ▼         ▼
┌─────────┐  ┌──────────────┐
│ Route to│  │ permission   │
│ Agent   │  │ blocked      │
│ Node    │  │ (Error)      │
└────┬────┘  └──────────────┘
     │
┌────┴────┬──────────┬──────────┐
▼         ▼          ▼          ▼
Creator  Reviewer  Approver   END
Agent    Agent     Agent
```

