### 7.2 HRMS Workflow Graph

**Location:** [`workflows/hrms_workflow/graph.py`](app/workflows/hrms_workflow/graph.py)

Same structure as RMS with HRMS-specific nodes and tools:
- `parse_intent_node` — Keyword-based persona inference
- `permission_check_node` — RBAC validation
- `creator_agent_node` — Define leave types, generate payslips
- `reviewer_agent_node` — Check leave balance, submit leave requests, view own payslip
