### 7.3 MRR Workflow Graph

**Location:** [`workflows/material_workflow/graph.py`](app/workflows/material_workflow/graph.py)

More complex graph with a **form state machine**:

```
Session Entry Router
    │
    ├── (new session) ──► parse_intent_node → permission_check_node
    │                                              │
    │                                        ┌─────┴─────┐
    │                                        ▼           ▼
    │                                   RBAC Route    Blocked
    │                                        │
    │                    ┌───────────────────┼──────────────┐
    │                    ▼                   ▼              ▼
    │              parse_user_input    welcome_node    Approver/Issuer
    │                    │
    │              ┌─────┴─────┐
    │              ▼           ▼
    │         handle_header  END (form)
    │              │
    │         handle_items
    │              │
    │     evaluate_and_route
    │              │
    │             END
    │
    └── (mid-form) ──► parse_user_input (skip RBAC)
```

**Graph Nodes:**
| Node | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `parse_intent_node` | LLM-based intent classification (CREATE/APPROVE/ISSUE) |
| `permission_check_node` | RBAC validation for MRR roles |
| `welcome_node` | Greet user based on their roles |
| `parse_user_input` | Parse widget submissions, update state |
| `handle_header` | Extract project details, show header form |
| `handle_items` | Add items via text, Excel upload, or item lookup |
| `evaluate_and_route` | Save to DB, determine routing (Manager vs ERP) |
| `approver_agent_node` | Show pending approvals for approver role |
| `issuer_agent_node` | Store issuer UI (stub) |

