## 10. Intent Inference (Keyword-Based)

### RMS Keywords

| Persona | Keywords |
|---------|----------|
| **Approver** | 'approve', 'reject', 'pending approvals', 'approval queue', 'sign off' |
| **Creator** | 'create task', 'new task', 'assign', 'plan task', 'add task' |
| **Reviewer** | 'log hours', 'log time', 'fill timesheet', 'my tasks', 'my entries', 'my timesheet', 'work hours', 'i worked' |
| **Query (routed by privilege)** | 'show', 'list', 'details', 'what tasks', 'what is', 'who is', 'how many hours', 'tell me', 'give me details', 'view', 'display', 'fetch' |

### HRMS Keywords

| Persona | Keywords |
|---------|----------|
| **Approver** | 'approve', 'reject', 'pending leaves', 'leave approvals', 'approve leave', 'approve request' |
| **Creator** | 'create leave type', 'new leave type', 'add leave type', 'define leave', 'generate payslip', 'create payslip' |
| **Reviewer** | 'log hours', 'log time', 'fill timesheet', 'my tasks', 'work hours', 'i worked' |

**Detection Priority:** APPROVER > CREATOR > REVIEWER > QUERY (routed by privilege) > DEFAULT (reviewer)

### MRR Intent Classification

Uses an LLM-based intent classifier agent instead of keyword matching:
| Intent | Required Role |
|--------|--------------|
| CREATE | mrr_creator |
| APPROVE | mrr_approver / erp_approver |
| ISSUE | str_issuer |
| UNKNOWN/GREETING | none |

