## 11. Security Layers

| Layer | Mechanism | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| **Authentication** | LDAP (prod) / DB lookup (dev) + JWT | Verify user identity |
| **Authorization** | RBAC (6-table schema) + persona checks | Control agent access |
| **Inbound Guardrails** | Keyword filtering (`FORBIDDEN_INBOUND`) | Block SQL injection, bypass attempts |
| **Outbound Guardrails** | Keyword redaction (`FORBIDDEN_OUTBOUND`) | Block confidential data leakage |
| **Department Isolation** | RAG filtering | Ensure dept-specific data access |
| **CORS** | Configurable origins | Control cross-origin requests |
| **Form Permission** | Persona-locked form handlers | Prevent unauthorized form submissions |
| **JWT Expiration** | 8-hour token lifetime | Limit session window |

